    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p>General information about integrators in RenderMan:<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN27/pages/542231922/Integrators\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542231922\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Integrators</a> </p><p>To add an integrator simply add one of the dedicated LOP node to create the corresponding USD integrator primitive.</p><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"2f27ba70-25d5-427a-9884-557f9a9a9a39\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>The previous ways (either via the dedicated tab on the Render Settings LOP or via the PxrIntegrator LOP) to add an integrator, while still supported, are deprecated.</p></div></div><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"integratorLOPs.png\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/575569950/integratorLOPs.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763047375908&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=529\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/575569950/integratorLOPs.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763047375908&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"658\" data-width=\"944\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"662962315\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"integratorLOPs.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"575569950\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"5\" data-media-id=\"7901de47-852e-49af-bb0d-1b1b91d2c58d\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/575569950/integratorLOPs.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763047375908&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=944&amp;height=658 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/575569950/integratorLOPs.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763047375908&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=529 1x\"></span><p>Then assign it to the render settings primitive:</p><ul><li><p>Houdini 20.5 and below: use a PxrAssign LOP (or the PxrAssignIntegrator alias) to assign an integrator primitive to a render settings primitive. The render settings primitive must exist before assignment.</p></li><li><p>Houdini 21.0 and above: while the PxrAssign LOP workflow is still valid, it is also possible to assign directly an integrator on the Render Settings LOP.</p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"assignIntegrator.png\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/575569950/assignIntegrator.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763047592436&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=443\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/575569950/assignIntegrator.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763047592436&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"637\" data-width=\"1091\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"664666151\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"assignIntegrator.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"575569950\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"5\" data-media-id=\"67408c86-ec95-40f8-b642-d0c53191f42d\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/575569950/assignIntegrator.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763047592436&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1091&amp;height=637 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/575569950/assignIntegrator.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763047592436&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=443 1x\"></span><p>If the assignment was properly done, in the Scene Graph, on the Render Settings primitive, the integrator primitive should be listed on the ri:integrator attribute in H21 and above or, on the outputs:ri:integrator attribute for H20.5 and below.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"intergratorAssignedH20.5.png\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/575569950/intergratorAssignedH20.5.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763049575531&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=398\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/575569950/intergratorAssignedH20.5.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763049575531&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"470\" data-width=\"896\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"665714691\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"intergratorAssignedH20.5.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"575569950\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"5\" data-media-id=\"99bb68ff-a7c8-4708-ae6a-3df1618ea01c\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/575569950/intergratorAssignedH20.5.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763049575531&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=896&amp;height=470 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/575569950/intergratorAssignedH20.5.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763049575531&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=398 1x\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"intergratorAssignedH21.png\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/575569950/intergratorAssignedH21.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763049589680&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=398\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/575569950/intergratorAssignedH21.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763049589680&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"470\" data-width=\"896\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"665780226\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"intergratorAssignedH21.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"575569950\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"5\" data-media-id=\"77bc5cb8-a0be-4908-a161-749888627db8\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/575569950/intergratorAssignedH21.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763049589680&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=896&amp;height=470 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/575569950/intergratorAssignedH21.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763049589680&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=398 1x\"></span><p />"
